race.comment: Competitive. EXPLICIT (5) was in the money two starts back at Randwick Kensington and following was beaten 2.25 lengths at Canterbury over 1550m. Peaks now and the step up in trip looks ideal. EUREKA REBEL (4) made good improvement placing over a mile at Kembla Grange. Ran into it well and is sure to keep improving. FREE AND FAST (6) disappointed this track/trip 3-weeks ago as favourite (vet cleared). Ran home strongly from the back over a mile at Kembla Grange prior and is worth another chance. ALMANZAS (1) was beaten 1.5 lengths in the EXPLICIT race. Led in that from the rails gate but has to skip over from the outside gate here. Has Bullock aboard, and that's a help. CANJUSTIFY (9) is an improver in the mix.
